snippet.title: FINAL FANTASY XI: May 2015 Version Update Trailer (US)
snippet.description:
Take a look into the sundry features that the May 2015 version update has in store for Vana'diel.

Teleport over to the official FINAL FANTASY XI site at:
http://www.finalfantasyxi.com

The Goddess's Gala website.
